{"tid":1773890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[128 行動post] 二零年 真普選 救手足 真普選 新口號 新力量 同我推上熱門","createTime":"2019-12-08T00:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T13:12:36.000Z","uid":21493,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f491225939ac5e5f391bd03d0bd30f33cb385e3b","tid":1773890,"uid":21493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T00:06:03.000Z","msg":"新口號 新力量<br />\n<br />\n我地承諾，會全力爭取2020真立法會普選，制裁功能組別參與人士，還我香港真自治。<br />\n<br />\n宜家仲有人講，爭取多啲功能組別議席。咁搞法，幾時先幫到被人告緊嘅手足？<br />\n<br />\n2020 立法會無，等2024？之後又係4年，4年又4年？<br />\n<br />\n手足坐完出嚟都未有。<br />\n<br />\n我地唔要永續抗爭，我地新一屆立法會就要真普選。<br />\n<br />\n大家，俾啲決心，一齊嗌，二零年，真普選，救手足，真普選。<br />\n<br />\n全力爭取2020真普選。"},{"pid":"a4856cb5327ab452fa90cd7456313bfdfba77cd3","tid":1773890,"uid":21493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T00:15:25.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"ea5563170e445d6414e7b07a48e8493523e87592","tid":1773890,"uid":21493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T00:19:53.000Z","msg":"[結果] 128 向全世界講 新口號 (二零年 真普選)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1772882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1772882</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7934d07d0075449c245f728508fb1f261a16dc97","tid":1773890,"uid":21493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T00:21:09.000Z","msg":"[徵求] 128新口號 向世界表達2020真普選訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1771382\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1771382</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"27e812aebc213ac585188df4065302b79aa51d39","tid":1773890,"uid":21493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T00:25:47.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"af5fd8902901cab1e7f294915bcd96e7b06fe0a1","tid":1773890,"uid":21493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T00:30:05.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"5ef87fe380e15e60ed603d1587586da65fe509b9","tid":1773890,"uid":100517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T00:30:35.